quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  41,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  41,1,Haa-Meeem
  41,2,( yeh kitaab khuday-e ) rehman o rahim ( ki taraf ) se utreen hai
  41,3,kitaab jis ki ayatain wazeh ( almaani ) hain ( yani ) quran arabi un logon ke liye jo samajh rakhtay hain
  41,4,jo basharat bhi sunataa hai aur khauf bhi dilaata hai lekin un mein se aksaron ne munh phair liya aur woh suntay hi nahi
  41,5,aur kehte hain ke jis cheez ki taraf tum hamein bulatay ho is se hamaray dil pardon mein hain aur hamaray kaanon mein boojh ( yani b_hrapn ) hai aur hamaray aur tumahray darmain parda hai to tum ( apna ) kaam karo hum ( apna ) kaam karte hain
  41,6,keh do ke mein bhi aadmi hon jaisay tum. ( haan ) mujh par yeh wahi aati hai ke tumhara mabood khuday-e wahid hai to seedhay isi ki taraf ( mutwajjah ) raho aur isi se mughfirat mango aur mushrikon par afsos hai
  41,7,jo zakaat nahi dete aur akhirat ke bhi qaail nahi
  41,8,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay un ke liye ( aisa ) sawab hai jo khatam hi nah ho
  41,9,kahokiya tum is se inkaar karte ho jis ne zameen ko do din mein pedakiya. aur ( buton ko ) is ka mad-muqabil banatay ho. wohi to saaray Jahan ka maalik hai
  41,10,aur isi ne zameen mein is ke oopar pahar banaye aur zameen mein barket rakhi aur is mein sab samaan maeeshat muqarrarkiya ( sab ) chaar din mein. ( aur tamam ) talabgaron ke liye yaksaa
  41,11,phir aasman ki taraf mutwajjah howa aur woh dhuwan tha to is ne is se aur zameen se farmaya ke dono aao ( khuwa ) khusi se khuwa na khushi se. unhon ne kaha ke hum khusi se atay hain
  41,12,phir do din mein saat aasman banaye aur har aasman mein is ( ke kaam ) ka hukum bheja aur hum ne aasman duniya ko charaghoon ( yani sitaron ) se muzayyankiya aur ( shaitano se ) mehfooz rakha. yeh zabardast ( aur ) khabardaar ke ( muqarrar kiye hue ) andazay hain
  41,13,phir agar yeh munh phair len to keh do ke mein tum ko aisay chngharh ( ke azaab ) se aagah karta hon jaisay Aad aur smod par chngharh ( ka azaab aaya tha )
  41,14,jab un ke paas paighambar un ke agay aur peechay se aeye ke khuda ke siwa ( kisi ki ) ibadat nah karo. kehnay lagey ke agar hamara perwar-digaar chahta to farishtay utaar deta so jo tum day kar beje gay ho hum is ko nahi mantay
  41,15,jo Aad they woh na-haq malik mein ghuroor karne lagey aur kehnay lagey ke hum se barh kar qowat mein kon hai?kiya unhon ne nahi dekha ke khuda jis ne un ko pedakiya woh un se qowat mein bohat barh kar hai. aur woh hamari aayton se inkaar karte rahay
  41,16,to hum ne bhi un par nahosat ke dinon mein zor ki howa chalaye taakay un ko duniya ki zindagi mein zillat ke azaab ka maza chakkha den. aur akhirat ka azaab to bohat hi zaleel karne wala hai aur ( is roz ) un ko madad bhi nah miley gi
  41,17,aur jo smod they un ko hum ne seedha rasta dikha diya tha magar unhon ne hadaayat ke muqablay mein andha dhund rehna pasandkiya to un ke aamaal ki saza mein kadak ne un ko aapkrha. aur woh zillat ka azaab tha
  41,18,aur jo imaan laaye aur parhaiz gari karte rahay un ko hum ne bacha liya
  41,19,aur jis din khuda ke dushman dozakh ki taraf chalaye jayen ge to tarteeb waar kar liyay jayen ge
  41,20,yahan taq ke jab is ke paas poanch jayen ge to un ke kaan aur ankhen aur chamray ( yani dosray aaza ) un ke khilaaf un ke aamaal ki shahadat den ge
  41,21,aur woh apne chumron ( yani aaza ) se kahin ge ke tum ne hamaray khilaaf kyun shahadat di? woh kahin ge ke jis khuda ne sab cheezon ko nutq bakhsha isi ne hum ko bhi goyai di aur isi ne tum ko pehli baar pedakiya tha aur isi ki taraf tum ko lout kar jana hai
  41,22,aur tum is ( baat ke khauf ) se to parda nahi karte they ke tumahray kaan aur tumhari ankhen aur chamray tumahray khilaaf shahadat den ge balkay tum yeh khayaal karte they ke khuda ko tumahray bohat se amlon ki khabar hi nahi
  41,23,aur isi khayaal ne jo tum apne perwar-digaar ke baray mein rakhtay they tum ko halaak kardiya aur tum khasara panay walon mein hogaye
  41,24,ab agar yeh sabr karen ge to un ka thikana dozakh hai. aur agar tauba karen ge to un ki tauba qubool nahi ki jaye gi
  41,25,aur hum ne ( shaitano ko ) un ka hum nasheen muqarrar kardiya tha to unhon ne un ke aglay aur pichlle aamaal un ko umdah kar dukhaay they aur jaanat aur insanon ki jamaten jo un se pehlay guzar chakain un par bhi khuda ( ke azaab ) ka wada poora hogaya. be shak yeh nuqsaan uthany walay hain
  41,26,aur kafir kehnay lagey ke is quran ko suna hi nah karo aur ( jab parhnay lagen to ) shore macha diya karo taakay tum ghalib raho
  41,27,so hum bhi kafiroon ko sakht azaab ke mazay chkhayin ge aur un ke buray amlon ki jo woh karte they saza den ge
  41,28,yeh khuda ke dushmanon ka badla hai ( yani ) dozakh. un ke liye isi mein hamesha ka ghar hai. yeh is ki saza hai ke hamari aayton se inkaar karte they
  41,29,aur kafir kahin ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar junoo aur insanon mein se jin logon ne hum ko gumraahkiya tha un ko hamein dikha ke hum un ko apne paon ke taley ( roond ) dalain taakay woh nihayat zaleel hon
  41,30,jin logon ne kaha ke hamara perwar-digaar khuda hai phir woh ( is par ) qaim rahay un par farishtay Utrain ge ( aur kahin ge ) ke nah khauf karo aur nah ghumnaak ho aur bahisht ki jis ka tum se wadakiya jata tha khusi maanao
  41,31,hum duniya ki zindagi mein bhi tumahray dost they aur akhirat mein bhi ( tumahray Rafeeq hain ). aur wahan jis ( Nemat ) ko tumhara jee chahay ga tum ko ( miley gi ) aur jo cheez talab karo ge tumahray liye ( mojood hogi )
  41,32,( yeh ) bakhsnay walay meharban ki taraf se mehmani hai
  41,33,aur is shakhs se baat ka acha kon ho sakta hai jo khuda ki taraf bulaye aur amal naik kere aur kahe ke mein musalman hon
  41,34,aur bhalai aur buraiee barabar nahi hosakti. to ( sakht kalami ka ) aisay tareeq se jawab do jo bohat acha ho ( aisa karne se tum dekho ge ) ke jis mein aur tum mein dushmani thi goya woh tumhara garam josh dost hai
  41,35,aur yeh baat un hi logon ko haasil hoti hai jo bardasht karne walay hain. aur un hi ko naseeb hoti hai jo barray sahib naseeb hain
  41,36,aur agar tumhe shetan ki janib se koi waswasa peda ho to khuda ki panah maang liya karo. be shak woh santa jaanta hai
  41,37,aur raat aur din aur Sooraj aur chaand is ki nshanyon mein se hain. tum log nah to Sooraj ko sajda karo aur nah chaand ko. balkay khuda hi ko sajda karo jis ne un cheezon ko pedakiya hai agar tum ko is ki ibadat Manzoor hai
  41,38,agar yeh log sar kashi karen to ( khuda ko bhi un ki parwa nahi ) jo ( farishtay ) tumahray perwar-digaar ke paas hain woh raat din is ki tasbeeh karte rehtay hain aur ( kabhi ) thkte hi nahi
  41,39,aur ( ae bande yeh ) isi ki qudrat ke namoonay hain ke to zameen ko dubi hui ( yani khushk ) daikhta hai. jab hum is par pani barsa dete hain to shadaab hojati aur phoolnay lagti hai to jis ne zameen ko zindahkiya wohi mardon ko zindah karne wala hai. be shak woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  41,40,jo log hamari aayton mein kaj raahi karte hain woh hum se posheeda nahi hain. bhala jo shakhs dozakh mein dala jaye woh behtar hai ya woh jo qayamat ke din aman o aman se aeye. ( to kher ) jo chaho so karlo. jo kuch tum karte ho woh is ko dekh raha hai
  41,41,jin logon ne nasiyaat ko nah maana jab woh un ke paas aayi. aur yeh to aik aliiiii rutba kitaab hai
  41,42,is par jhoot ka dakhal nah agay se ho sakta hai nah peechay se. ( aur ) Dana ( aur ) khoobiyon walay ( khuda ) ki aُtari hui hai
  41,43,tum se wohi baatein kahin jati hain jo tum se pehlay aur payghambaroon se kahi gayi theen. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar bakhash dainay wala bhi aur azaab alim dainay wala bhi hai
  41,44,aur agar hum is quran ko ghair zabaan arab mein ( nazil ) karte to yeh log kehte ke is ki ayatain ( hamari zabaan mein ) kyun khol kar bayan nahi ki gayeen.kiya ( khoob ke quran to ) ajmi aur ( mukhatib ) arabi. keh do ke jo imaan laatay hain un ke liye ( yeh ) hadaayat aur Shifa hai. aur jo imaan nahi laatay un ke kaanon mein gharani ( yani b_hrapn ) hai aur yeh un ke haq mein ( mojab ) نابینائی hai. gharani ke sabab un ko ( goya ) daur jagah se aawaz di jati hai
  41,45,aur hum ne moose ko kitaab di to is mein ikhtilaafkiya gaya. aur agar tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se aik baat pehlay nah thehr chuki hoti to un mein faisla kardiya jata. aur yeh is ( quran ) se shak mein ulajh rahay hain
  41,46,jo naik kaam kere ga to apne liye. aur jo buray kaam kere ga to un ka zarrar isi ko hoga. aur tumhara perwar-digaar bundon par zulm karne wala nahi
  41,47,qayamat ke ilm ka hawala isi ki taraf diya jata hai ( yani qayamat ka ilm isi ko hai ) aur nah to phal ga bhoon se nikaltay hain aur nah koi madah haamla hoti aur nah janati hai magar is ke ilm se. aur jis din woh un ko pukare ga ( aur kahe ga ) ke mere shareek kahan hain to woh kahin ge ke hum tujh se arz karte hain ke hum mein se kisi ko ( un ki ) khabar hi nahi
  41,48,aur jin ko pehlay woh ( khuda ke siwa ) puraka karte they ( sab ) un se gayab ho jaien ge aur woh yaqeen karlen ge ke un ke liye mukhlasi nahi
  41,49,ensaan bhalai ki duayen karta karta to thakta nahi aur agar takleef poanch jati hai to na umeed hojata aur aas toar baithta hai
  41,50,aur agar takleef pounchanay ke baad hum is ko apni rehmat ka maza chukhate hain to kehta hai ke yeh to mera haq tha aur mein nahi khayaal karta ke qayamat barpaa ho. aur agar ( qayamat sach mach bhi ho aur ) mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lotaya bhi jaoon to mere liye is ke haan bhi khushhali hai. pas kafir jo amalkiya karte woh hum un ko zaroor jaatein ge aur un ko sakht azaab ka maza chkhayin ge
  41,51,aur jab hum ensaan par karam karte hain to munh mourr laita hai aur pehlu phair kar chal deta hai. aur jab is ko takleef pahunchti hai to lambi lambi duayen karne lagta hai
  41,52,kaho ke bhala dekho agar yeh ( quran ) khuda ki taraf se ho phir tum is se inkaar karo to is se barh kar kon gumraah hai jo ( haq ki ) parlay darjay ki mukhalfat mein ho
  41,53,hum anqareeb un ko atraaf ( aalam ) mein bhi aur khud un ki zaat mein bhi apni nishanain deikhein ge yahan taq ke un par zahir hojaye ga ke ( quran ) haq hai.kiya tum ko yeh kaafi nahi ke tumhara perwar-digaar har cheez se khabardaar hai
  41,54,dekho yeh apne perwar-digaar ke rubaroo haazir honay se shak mein hain. sun rakho ke woh har cheez par ihata kiye hue hai
